             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
              <h3>
               Notes
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Keep in mind that it is not relevant which team wins. Only the margin of victory matters.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              A victory margin of 0 and a draw are the same thing.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              There are 100 cents in a dollar.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              If the company has to pay more than it receives, the day's net gain will be negative.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
              <h3>
               Constraints
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <b>
               amounts
              </b>
              will contain between 1 and 50 elements, inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
