              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <b>
               finalResult
              </b>
              will be between 0 and n-1, inclusive, where n is the number of elements in
              <b>
               amounts
              </b>
              .
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Each element of
              <b>
               amounts
              </b>
              will be between 0 and 5000, inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
